line_1: But he who wrote the Life of TOMMY THUMB.
line_2: Compar'd with thee, be all life-writers dumb,

line_1: Writing ne'er cramp'd the sinews of my thumb,
line_2: Nor barbarous birch e'er brush'd my tender bum.
